import React from 'react';
import {Menu, Message} from 'semantic-ui-react';

export default () => {
  return (
    <Menu tabular
      size='massive'
    >
      <Menu.Item header
        name='Break Randomizer'
      />
      <Menu.Menu
        position='right'
      >
        <Menu.Item
          name='Main'
          link='/main'
        />
        <Menu.Item
          name='Edit'
          link='/edit'
        />
      </Menu.Menu>
    </Menu>
  );
}
